snippet: A scoreless draw with Kazakhstan guaranteed Iceland a place in the 2016 European Championship as one of the top two finishers in Group A, along with the Czech Republic.
abstract: Iceland draws, 0-0, with Kazakhstan to win place as one of top two finishers in Group A of 2016 European Championship of soccer.
lead_paragraph: A scoreless draw with Kazakhstan guaranteed Iceland a place in the 2016 European Championship as one of the top two finishers in Group A, along with the Czech Republic.
